parameters:
A photo is displayed in a picture frame. Three people, Yuuka, a slightly
older but beautiful woman, and a young woman who looks very similar to
Yuuka, are standing shoulder to shoulder with smiles that suggest they are
very close.
(Yuuka-san, her older sister, and their mother.. I guess?)

Chains and handcuffs are fixed to the wall. I wonder if someone was
restrained here and brought to climax multiple times with sex toys..

"I-I thought this was just a normal house.. why is there a room like
this..?"

There is a window for lighting. Hinori notices that it looks like frosted
glass at first glance, but from a certain angle, it becomes almost
transparent.

"Oh, wait.. It's hard to notice that the inside is bright, but can you see
through it from the outside..?"

Various sizes of sex toys such as vibrators split into two, anal beads, and
rotors are carelessly and abundantly placed. The strong scent of female
sexuality wafts through the air, making it impossible to hide the extent to
which the sex toys have been used.
"All of these are.. sex toys, right..? W-Why are there so many..?"

"(Could it be that Reiji is Yuuka-san's trainer..? Wait, if that's the
case, does that mean Reiji is also in this house..?)"

There is a tablet-shaped device placed by the pillow. It's a common model
that can be seen frequently in the outside world.

(Does this belong to Yuuka-san..? It doesn't seem to be connected to the
internet, but I wonder what she's using it for..)

Two futons are laid out side by side, fitting together perfectly and
alluringly. Hinori's sensitive nose catches a faint, musky scent. Has
someone made love on these futons many times before?

(This feels kind of lewd.. with Yuuka-san.. I wonder whose futon is the
other one?)

"I'll make tea right away, so could you wait and look around here for a
bit?"
